{"Id":867460,"Title":"浣溪沙·戊午春感四首","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"黄侃","Context":"春到人间愁与俱。残梅谢了柳黄初。诗怀今昔不相如。羸病不禁三日醉，乱离难得一家娱。浮名懒计总区区。寥落新春白袷衣。在家沈醉出忘归。感时伤命两俱非。金勒不来花正发，玉珰难寄雁仍飞。轻将双泪洒斜晖。士女熙春足胜游。羸躯到春见春羞。强因山色一登楼。芳草自然堪下泪，萱花何事可忘忧。此情分付醉时讴。海思云悲亦易平。筐床夜夜待钟鸣。镜中容色未妨更。远信不从苍雁索，残书难与白鱼争。预愁明日酒瓶倾。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"浣溪沙","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"0a4aae7d7cc994b2a7c14e311f1d4719","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5089857,"Sentence":"春到人间愁与俱。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chūn dào rén jiān chóu yú jū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089858,"Sentence":"残梅谢了柳黄初。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"cán méi xiè 了liu huáng chū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089859,"Sentence":"诗怀今昔不相如。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shī huái jīn xī bú xiāng rú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089860,"Sentence":"羸病不禁三日醉，乱离难得一家娱。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"léi bìng bú jīn sān rì zuì ，luàn lǐ nán dé yī gū yú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089861,"Sentence":"浮名懒计总区区。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fú mǐng lǎn jì zǒng ōu ōu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089862,"Sentence":"寥落新春白袷衣。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"liáo là xīn chūn bái jiá yī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089863,"Sentence":"在家沈醉出忘归。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zài gū shěn zuì chū wàng guī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089864,"Sentence":"感时伤命两俱非。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gǎn shǐ shāng mìng liǎng jū fēi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5089865,"Sentence":"金勒不来花正发，玉珰难寄雁仍飞。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jīn lè bú lái huā zhēng fā ，yù dāng nán jì yàn réng fēi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":nu